  "description": "A vibrant nighttime cityscape dominated by a long, illuminated bridge and a spectacular fireworks display. The bridge, with its multiple arches and lights, spans a dark body of water, connecting to a densely packed urban landscape. The city skyline is ablaze with warm, golden lights, punctuated by taller, modern buildings. Above the city, a burst of fireworks creates a dazzling spectacle, with streaks of white, blue, and red illuminating the night sky. The composition features a high-angle perspective, capturing the expanse of the city and the impressive length of the bridge.",
